aa(lp253
VHow can a boiling river exist like this?
p254
aVI've asked geothermal experts and volcanologists for years,
p255
aVand I'm still unable to find another non-volcanic geothermal system
p256
aVof this magnitude.
p257
aVIt's unique.
p258
aVIt's special on a global scale.
p259
aVSo, still \u2014 how does it work?
p260
aVWhere do we get this heat?
p261
aVThere's still more research to be done
p262
aVto better constrain the problem and better understand the system,
p263
aVbut from what the data is telling us now,
p264
aVit looks to be the result of a large hydrothermal system.
